, \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2038, \"end\": 2049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bassa_Mawem\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bassa Mawem\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bassa_Mawem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bassa_Mawem\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"youthful zeal\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2027}, {\"ngram\": \"all the wisdom\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"wherewithal\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mawem's participation at World Cups dates back to 2006-in fact, Mawem's comp career predates the IFSC itself, as the governing body of World Cups during Mawem's rookie year was the UIAA.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2243, \"end\": 2247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_of_Sport_Climbing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9348250098586e-52, \"text\": \"IFSC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_of_Sport_Climbing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_of_Sport_Climbing\"}, {\"begin\": 2327, \"end\": 2331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Climbing_and_Mountaineering_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4052390159740962e-51, \"text\": \"UIAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Climbing_and_Mountaineering_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Climbing_and_Mountaineering_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mawem's participation\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"World Cups\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"Mawem's comp career\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2229}, {\"ngram\": \"the governing body\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2277}, {\"ngram\": \"World Cups\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"Mawem's rookie year\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mawem has won multiple speed World Cups over the years, but, more importantly, he took part in the Tokyo Olympics several years ago-which enhanced his level of big-event experience.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mawem\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple speed World Cups\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"his level\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2489}, {\"ngram\": \"big-event experience\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, those Tokyo Olympics were disastrous for Mawem, as he tore his bicep near the end of the qualifying round (although he did manage to clock an Olympic speed record of 5.45 seconds prior to the injury derailment).\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2550}, {\"ngram\": \"Mawem\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2576}, {\"ngram\": \"his bicep\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2598}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2611}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualifying round\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic speed record\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2692}, {\"ngram\": \"5.45 seconds\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2708}, {\"ngram\": \"the injury derailment\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fortunately, he is fully healed and better than ever, evidenced by a first-place finish at the European Continental event last year that earned him a ticket to the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a first-place finish\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"the European Continental event\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2863}, {\"ngram\": \"a ticket\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Career highlight (thus far):A World Cup victory in Moscow, Russia, in 2019, saw Bassa Mawem beat China's Long Cao, Iran's Reza Alipour Shenazandifard, Indonesia's Aspar Aspar, and others who were among the fastest men in the world (and still are).\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 3170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2953, \"end\": 2962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Alpine_Ski_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9418697086380151, \"rank\": 0.06171797188070094, \"text\": \"World Cup\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Alpine_Ski_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Alpine_Ski_World_Cup\"}, {\"begin\": 2974, \"end\": 2980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7518309023998194e-16, \"text\": \"Moscow\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\"}, {\"begin\": 2982, \"end\": 2988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.980340374837517, \"rank\": 0.017888148910303478, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3003, \"end\": 3014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bassa_Mawem\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bassa Mawem\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bassa_Mawem\", \"dbpedi