rom\": 8086, \"to\": 8104}, {\"ngram\": \"the current national record\", \"from\": 8131, \"to\": 8158}, {\"ngram\": \"6.30 seconds\", \"from\": 8162, \"to\": 8174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But as she claimed her space in the United States' record book, she also made her presence known at the global level, particularly by earning World Cup medals in 2022 and 2023 (and a gold medal at Salt Lake City earlier this year).\", \"from\": 8176, \"to\": 8407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8212, \"end\": 8225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9994685084155996, \"rank\": 0.0005016532304942573, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 8373, \"end\": 8387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.9280813002532233, \"rank\": 0.07749180995995396, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her space\", \"from\": 8195, \"to\": 8204}, {\"ngram\": \"her presence\", \"from\": 8254, \"to\": 8266}, {\"ngram\": \"the global level\", \"from\": 8276, \"to\": 8292}, {\"ngram\": \"World Cup medals\", \"from\": 8318, \"to\": 8334}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 8357, \"to\": 8369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's yet to clock a time comparable to Miroslaw's personal best of 6.24 seconds, but Hunt is extremely close.\", \"from\": 8408, \"to\": 8518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 8427, \"to\": 8433}, {\"ngram\": \"6.24 seconds\", \"from\": 8476, \"to\": 8488}, {\"ngram\": \"Hunt\", \"from\": 8494, \"to\": 8498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If Hunt lines up against Miroslaw at the Paris Olympics, it could very likel