: 10244}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure-cooker\", \"from\": 10248, \"to\": 10267}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 10271, \"to\": 10282}, {\"ngram\": \"her times\", \"from\": 10292, \"to\": 10301}, {\"ngram\": \"records\", \"from\": 10317, \"to\": 10324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a time, particularly in the lead-up to the Tokyo Olympics several years ago, when Piper Kelly wastheface of American speed climbing.\", \"from\": 10327, \"to\": 10469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10445, \"end\": 10453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"score\": 0.9621749816318166, \"rank\": 0.039311995127931536, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6631808\", \"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 10337, \"to\": 10343}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead-up\", \"from\": 10361, \"to\": 10372}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 10376, \"to\": 10394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She owned the national record, and she was adjusting to the three-discipline Combined format while vying for a ticket to those Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 10470, \"to\": 10612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10597, \"end\": 10611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4947813009893152e-24, \"text\": \"Tokyo Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the national record\", \"from\": 10480, \"to\": 10499}, {\"ngram\": \"the three-discipline Combined format\", \"from\": 10526, \"to\": 10562}, {\"ngram\": \"a ticket\", \"from\": 10579, \"to\": 10587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But then she dislocated her shoulder, which proved to be an unfortunate termination to those Olympic ambitions.\", \"from\": 10613, \"to\": 10724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her shoulder\", \"from\": 10637, \"to\": 10649}, {\"ngram\": \"an unfortunate termination\", \"from\": 10670, \"to\": 10696}, {\"ngram\": \"those Olympic ambitions\", \"from\": 10700, \"to\": 10723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her climbing career halted for a long time and she was still recovering from multiple dislocations-and surgery-when hype for the Paris Olympics began years later.\", \"from\": 10725, \"to\": 10887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her climbing career\", \"from\": 10725, \"to\": 10744}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 10756, \"to\": 10767}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple dislocations\", \"from\": 10802, \"to\": 10823}, {\"ngram\": \"surgery\", \"from\": 10828, \"to\": 10835}, {\"ngram\": \"hype\", \"from\": 10841, \"to\": 10845}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 10850, \"to\": 10868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many fans did not want to admit it, but Kelly's chances of returning to her post-injury level seemed unlikely.\", \"from\": 10888, \"to\": 10998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10928, \"end\": 10933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"score\": 0.981698874750669, \"rank\": 0.018642300322238126, \"text\": \"Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many fans\", \"from\": 10888, \"to\": 10897}, {\"ngram\": \"her post-injury level\", \"from\": 10960, \"to\": 10981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, Kelly re-entered the World Cup scene and showed remarkable consistency.\", \"from\": 10999, \"to\": 11075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11004, \"end\": 11009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"score\": 0.981698874750669, \"rank\": 0.018642300322238126, \"text\": \"Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour